# Backend AI Interaction Rules

## Code Organization
- Follow Symfony 7 best practices
- Organize code by domain (Admin, HR, Student, etc.)
- Use proper service/repository patterns
- Follow established folder structure

## API Development
- Use proper HTTP methods
- Include proper validation
- Implement proper error handling
- Follow REST conventions
- Document with OpenAPI/Swagger

## Security
- Follow CORS policies
- Validate user permissions
- Sanitize inputs

## Database
- Use Doctrine annotations/attributes correctly
- Include proper database indexes
- Follow naming conventions
- Include migration files